 DeVilbiss Gordon (X-prefix), Fred Hooker Gordon III (HD-prefix, infant Boston meningioma), Lucius Robinson 'Bob' Gordon (HD-prefix, NOTABLE), Marie Antoinette 'Tony' Townson Gordon (X-prefix), William Ward Gordon (HD-prefix), Emilie Wolcott Gordon (X-prefix), William Ward Gordon Jr (HD-prefix back in original Lot 61 Range 2). Largest Hooker-tree concentration after Cypress Lawn SF.","hooker_connections":["H03434","H03437","H03892","HD3261","HD3262","HD3263","HD3264","HD3265","HD3266","HD3267","HD3268","HD3275","HD3276","HD3277","HD3279","HD3280","HD3400","HD3401","HD3834","HD3836","HD3842","I00339","X02281","X02282","X02283","X02284","X02290","X02293","X02295","HD3870","HD3871","HD3872","HD3873","HD3874","HD3875","I00490","I00491","I00492","I00494","X03270","X03271","X03272","X03273","X03274"],"person_ids":["HD3870","HD3871","HD3872","HD3873","HD3874","HD3875","I00490","I00491","I00492","I00494"]},"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}